Class Username

Object
  mireka.login.Username

@ThreadSafe
public class Username
extends Object

case-insensitive user name, where case-insensitivity is defined by the en_US locale. Note that in a general case case-insensitivity depends on locale, but basic SMTP, without Unicode extensions, only allows ASCII local parts in mail addresses.
